        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "When on, opted-in notes re-run their queries on their cadence (hourly sweep while Obsidian is open). `motherduck` blocks make network calls to your MotherDuck workspace during these refreshes; `duckdb` blocks stay local.",
          "target": "开启后，已启用的笔记会按其频率重新运行查询（Obsidian打开时每小时扫描一次）。`motherduck` 代码块在这些刷新期间会向您的MotherDuck工作区发起网络调用；`duckdb` 代码块则保持本地运行。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Frees WASM worker memory once the hourly sweep finishes. Trade-off: the next interactive query pays ~1-2s of init cost. Recommended on for memory-heavy queries.",
          "target": "在每小时扫描完成后释放WASM工作线程内存。权衡：下一次交互式查询将承担约1-2秒的初始化成本。建议在内存密集型查询时开启。"
        },
        {
          "type": "CallExpression",
          "name": "setDesc",
          "source": "Sweeps every note in the vault that has a SQL block, ignoring cadence and frontmatter opt-in. Available even when auto-refresh is off.",
